Package: vyos-ipblock
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: VyOS IP Blocklist Generator <wieger.bontekoe@productsup.com>
Installed-Size: 58
Depends: python3, python3-requests, sudo, nftables
Recommends: cron
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/productsupcom/vyos-ipblock-generator
Description: VyOS IP blocklist generator from threat intelligence sources
 This package provides a tool to generate and apply IP blocklists to VyOS
 nftables from multiple threat intelligence sources including Emerging Threats,
 Binary Defense, and AbuseIPDB.
 .
 Features:
  - Fetches blocklists from multiple threat intelligence sources
  - Deduplication and optimization of IP ranges
  - Whitelist support to protect your own networks
  - Dry-run mode for testing
  - Comprehensive logging
  - Integration with VyOS nftables
